''kaeh do in hassreto<U+0144> se kah<U+012B><U+0144> aur j<U+0101> bas'<U+00E9><U+0144>''<br>
''itn<U+012B> jageh kah<U+0101><U+0144> h<U+00E9> dil-e-d<U+0101>Ghd<U+0101>r  m<U+00E9><U+0144>''<br>
